text: Danaher is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Declan Danaher, English Rugby union player * Kevin Danaher (Caoimhín Ó Danachair), (1913–2002), author and prominent Irish folklorist * Kevin Danaher (activist), Ph.D. in sociology, author of several books on Green Economy ==See also== * Danaher Corporation, a company headquartered in Washington, D.C.
